<p>A paragraph with <em>emphasis</em>, <strong>strong emphasis</strong>,
and <code>inline literal</code> text.</p>
<p>A second paragraph that spans two source lines joined by a soft
break.</p>
<p>Escapes keep a literal *asterisk* intact, and an inline literal can
